# Mobile App Refactoring — Walkthrough

## Summary

Refactored the entire `mobile/src/` codebase (21 source files) to eliminate redundancy, remove dead code, simplify logic, and wire up 6 placeholder screens to their existing API functions. **TypeScript compilation passes with 0 errors.**

