| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [types/index.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/SurveyCorps/Projects/estate-practice/mobile/src/types/index.ts) | Centralized type definitions (was duplicated across 3 API files) |
| [utils/formatters.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/SurveyCorps/Projects/estate-practice/mobile/src/utils/formatters.ts) | `formatCurrency`, `formatDate`, `capitalize` utilities |
| [utils/errors.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/SurveyCorps/Projects/estate-practice/mobile/src/utils/errors.ts) | Shared `getErrorMessage` for extracting API error messages |
| [constants/styles.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/SurveyCorps/Projects/estate-practice/mobile/src/constants/styles.ts) | Shared `screenStyles` + `tabBarScreenOptions` |
| [screens/auth/authStyles.ts](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Desktop/SurveyCorps/Projects/estate-practice/mobile/src/screens/auth/authStyles.ts) | Shared auth form styles (Login + Register) |

